entation, adversarial regularization) are most needed. By reframing overfitting detection as a learned similarity task grounded in fairness-sensitive contrastive examples, this work advances both model interpretability and ethical AI auditing, offering a deployable plugin for real-time representation health monitoring in production NLP systems.",
